title: Batman Animated Soundtrack Collection ( Shirley Walker etc )
description:
A collection of soundtracks from the Batman Animated universe, namely:


- Mask Of Phantasm OST ~ by Shirley Walker (animated movie)
- Subzero OST ~ by Michael McCuistion (animated movie)
- Batman Beyond ~ Return of the Joker by Kristopher Carter (animated movie)
- Batman Beyond OST ~ Shirley Walker etc (tv series)
- Batman The Animated Series ~ Shirley Walker etc (very rare collection of suites from the original series)
- The New Batman & Superman Adventures ~ Lolita Ritmanis & Michael McCuistion (another rare collection from 3 episode&#039;s, 1x Batman and 2x Superman)
